d yet realistic and real changes. A comparison with state-of-the-art\nchange detection methods evidences the accuracy of the proposed strategy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 Jul 2018 10:02:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Sep 2019 13:44:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
